tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻既先會帶港幣去日本<br />\n<br />\n唱定YEN先是常識吧?</blockquote><br />\n已經唱咗喇，屋企人係低價嘅時候唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441c4871284bc81d4f5ac8cf3a30608dc21efa9b","tid":188281,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2個人一萬我都覺得夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你餐餐都極高級魚生加a5和牛啦</blockquote><br />\n諗住一兩餐豪食，其他平平地都好好食"},{"pid":"3b4c3ba82e3e9df10874ea135ef27825a95fdd77","tid":188281,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶左28萬yen去8日<br />\n結果返到香港就得返3000yen <br />\n已經買左usj ticket fastpass <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你豪買豪玩豪食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8cb0bd624fa6d95d18a23d7e8952f7c68c2a4d","tid":188281,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我帶15萬円去10日，豪食唔算豪玩最尾剩4萬，睇你自己想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇買嘢？"},{"pid":"2f5c7d499106f7a10e6017e8f1308acb553a0a60","tid":188281,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>傻既先會帶港幣去日本<br />\n<br />\n唱定YEN先是常識吧?</blockquote><br />\n已經唱咗喇，屋企人係低價嘅時候唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己係唱定啲<br />\n到時唔夠再海外提款"},{"pid":"2e3e605704e0da50470d6e5f4f21a192c1503af1","tid":188281,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2個人一萬我都覺得夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你餐餐都極高級魚生加a5和牛啦</blockquote><br />\n諗住一兩餐豪食，其他平平地都好好食</blockquote><br />\n應該夠嘅<br />\n不過原來我睇錯topic<br />\n我1萬係用7日，但包埋由大阪去東京嘅晚間車錢<br />\n我自己最後悔係食咗個ok 貴嘅烤肉<br />\n啲肉其實好靚，但自己唔識燒<br />\n寧願去神戶食多幾次和牛"},{"pid":"ba131220bd30216ba2546896e9d60d84f40400c6","tid":188281,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:13:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩左5日4夜 唔計機票酒店只係用左3500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平飲平食？<br />\n我都諗緊6日5夜要帶幾多好<br />\n手信應該淨買一兩份 買下藥妝<br />\n主要係食 諗住一日起碼食四五餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fda76e885115bdb6ca9acd1de619779a7cab44","tid":188281,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帶左28萬yen去8日<br />\n結果返到香港就得返3000yen <br />\n已經買左usj ticket fastpass <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你豪買豪玩豪食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中間車錢食野錢好貴呀.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fc98b56cdbd5118d6072b442742585fd23ffb7","tid":188281,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"對我嚟講唔夠"},{"pid":"31573fcdd36e673b8991256478fd9b72784aa26a","tid":188281,"uid":76349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"唔好去飛田新地，去左多多錢都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}